<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://vapebienhoa.com/bo-thuoc-la-bang-thuoc-mieng-dan-va-keo-gum/">B&#7887; thu&#7889;c l&aacute; b&#7857;ng thu&#7889;c, mi&#7871;ng d&aacute;n v&agrave; k&#7865;o gum</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://vapebienhoa.com">VAPE BI&Ecirc;N H&Ograve;A</a>.</p></div>";s:7:"content";s:22110:"<div><p><strong>B&#7887; thu&#7889;c l&aacute;</strong> kh&ocirc;ng bao gi&#7901; d&#7877; d&agrave;ng, nh&#432;ng s&#7921; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&#7911;a c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; h&#7895; tr&#7907; &#273;&atilde; gi&uacute;p vi&#7879;c t&#7915; b&#7887; c&#417;n nghi&#7879;n nicotine c&#7911;a nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i nghi&#7879;n thu&#7889;c l&aacute; tr&#7903; n&ecirc;n d&#7877; d&agrave;ng h&#417;n bao gi&#7901; h&#7871;t.<br>
C&aacute;c nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u ch&#7881; ra r&#7857;ng v&#7899;i s&#7921; h&#7895; tr&#7907; c&#7911;a thu&#7889;c v&agrave; c&aacute;c li&#7879;u ph&aacute;p thay th&#7871; nicotine, nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i nghi&#7879;n thu&#7889;c c&oacute; th&#7875; c&oacute; c&#417; h&#7897;i b&#7887; thu&#7889;c th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng t&#259;ng g&#7845;p &#273;&ocirc;i, th&#7853;m ch&iacute; l&agrave; g&#7845;p ba l&#7847;n. M&#7897;t s&#7889; ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p &#273;i&#7873;u tr&#7883; c&ograve;n gi&uacute;p gi&#7843;m thi&#7875;u vi&#7879;c t&#259;ng c&acirc;n khi cai thu&#7889;c &ndash; m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng l&iacute; do khi&#7871;n nhi&#7873;u con nghi&#7879;n t&#7915; b&#7887; vi&#7879;c cai thu&#7889;c.</p>
<p>C&ugrave;ng v&#7899;i s&#7921; gia t&#259;ng c&aacute;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n cho vi&#7879;c cai thu&#7889;c, ng&agrave;y nay c&aacute;c b&aacute;c s&#297; c&oacute; th&#7875; t&#7841;o ra c&aacute;c li&#7879;u tr&igrave;nh cai thu&#7889;c c&aacute; nh&acirc;n ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i nhu c&#7847;u v&agrave; s&#7903; th&iacute;ch c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i h&uacute;t thu&#7889;c.</p>
<p><strong>V&#7853;y ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p n&agrave;o ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i b&#7841;n? D&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y l&agrave; m&#7897;t li&#7879;u tr&igrave;nh v&agrave; thu&#7889;c gi&uacute;p b&#7887; thu&#7889;c l&aacute;:</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Li&#7879;u ph&aacute;p thay th&#7871; Nicotine<br>
&#272;&acirc;y l&agrave; m&#7897;t &yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n. B&#7857;ng vi&#7879;c gi&uacute;p ng&#432;&#7901;i nghi&#7879;n thu&#7889;c qu&#7843;n l&yacute; c&#417;n nghi&#7879;n c&#7911;a h&#7885;, li&#7879;u ph&aacute;p thay th&#7871; nicotine &#273;&#432;a ra c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i thu&#7889;c &ndash; d&#432;&#7907;c ph&#7849;m thay th&#7871; l&agrave;nh m&#7841;nh v&agrave; an to&agrave;n h&#417;n thu&#7889;c l&aacute;. M&#7897;t c&aacute;ch l&yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng, nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&atilde; cai thu&#7889;c th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&#7843;m d&#7847;n s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng nicotine ho&#7863;c ch&#7845;m d&#7913;t vi&#7879;c d&ugrave;ng li&#7879;u ph&aacute;p thay th&#7871; nicotine c&ugrave;ng l&uacute;c khi h&#7885; t&#7915; b&#7887; th&oacute;i quen h&uacute;t thu&#7889;c. Cho d&ugrave; c&oacute; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng trong th&#7901;i gian d&agrave;i th&igrave; c&aacute;c ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p &#273;i&#7873;u tr&#7883; thay th&#7871; nicotine c&#361;ng an to&agrave;n h&#417;n h&uacute;t thu&#7889;c nhi&#7873;u. T&#7927; l&#7879; ng&#432;&#7901;i b&#7887; thu&#7889;c th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng khi s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p n&agrave;y dao &#273;&#7897;ng t&#7915; 19% &#273;&#7871;n 26%.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a class="dt-single-image" href="http://vapebienhoa.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/keo-gum-nicotin.jpeg" data-dt-img-description=""><img class="wp-image-36087 aligncenter" src="http://vapebienhoa.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/keo-gum-nicotin.jpeg" alt="keo-gum-nicotin" width="598" height="531"></a>K&#7865;o gum nicotin c&oacute; th&#7875; h&#7895; tr&#7907; cai thu&#7889;c l&aacute;</em></p>
<p>N&#7871;u tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&acirc;y b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; t&#7915;ng t&#7915; b&#7887; vi&#7879;c cai thu&#7889;c v&agrave; th&#7845;t b&#7841;i b&#7903;i v&igrave; s&#7913;c h&uacute;t c&#7911;a nicotine qu&aacute; l&#7899;n, ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p thay th&#7871; nicotine c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&uacute;p b&#7841;n. K&#7865;o gum, k&#7865;o ng&#7853;m v&agrave; c&aacute;c mi&#7871;ng d&aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&aacute;n r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u. Thu&#7889;c x&#7883;t m&#361;i v&agrave; thu&#7889;c h&iacute;t c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng theo toa. K&#7865;o gum v&agrave; k&#7865;o ng&#7853;m d&ugrave;ng r&#7845;t ti&#7879;n l&#7907;i, ng&#432;&#7901;i nghi&#7879;n thu&#7889;c ch&#7881; c&#7847;n b&#7887; ch&uacute;ng v&agrave;o mi&#7879;ng thay cho thu&#7889;c l&aacute;. M&#7897;t s&#7889; ng&#432;&#7901;i nghi&#7879;n thu&#7889;c th&iacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng thu&#7889;c h&iacute;t v&igrave; c&#7843;m gi&aacute;c khi d&ugrave;ng n&oacute; gi&#7889;ng nh&#432; khi &#273;ang h&uacute;t m&#7897;t &#273;i&#7871;u thu&#7889;c l&aacute;. T&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c c&aacute;ch tr&ecirc;n &#273;&#7873;u c&oacute; t&aacute;c d&#7909;ng t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng nhau v&agrave; ch&uacute;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p v&#7899;i nhau. Th&#7853;t v&#7853;y, c&aacute;c b&#7857;ng ch&#7913;ng ch&#7881; ra r&#7857;ng vi&#7879;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p mi&#7871;ng d&aacute;n ng&#432;&#7901;i thu&#7889;c v&#7899;i thu&#7889;c h&iacute;t, k&#7865;o gum hay thu&#7889;c x&#7883;t n&acirc;ng cao t&#7927; l&#7879; b&#7887; thu&#7889;c trong th&#7901;i gian d&agrave;i. Nh&#432;ng khi s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c li&#7879;u ph&aacute;p thay th&#7871; nicotine b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c h&uacute;t thu&#7889;c. B&#7841;n ph&#7843;i v&#7913;t b&#7887; thu&#7889;c l&aacute; &#273;i tr&#432;&#7899;c khi b&#7841;n th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n b&#7845;t c&#7913; ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p thay th&#7871; nicotine n&agrave;o.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a class="dt-single-image" href="http://vapebienhoa.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/zero-nicotine4.jpg" data-dt-img-description=""><img class=" wp-image-36088 aligncenter" src="http://vapebienhoa.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/zero-nicotine4.jpg" alt="zero-nicotine4" width="527" height="298"></a>Mi&#7871;ng d&aacute;n nicotin</em></p>
<p><strong>L&#7901;i khuy&ecirc;n c&#7911;a chuy&ecirc;n gia:</strong></p>
<p>Ti&#7871;n s&#297; Scott McIntosh &ndash; Ph&oacute; Gi&aacute;o s&#432; t&#7841;i Trung t&acirc;m Y t&#7871; C&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng v&agrave; Y t&#7871; D&#7921; ph&ograve;ng c&#7911;a &#272;&#7841;i h&#7885;c Rochester, New York; Gi&aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c Trung t&acirc;m Khai thu&#7889;c v&ugrave;ng Greater Rochester khuy&ecirc;n r&#7857;ng: &ldquo;&#272;&#7915;ng qu&aacute; n&oacute;ng v&#7897;i &#273;&#7875; d&#7915;ng li&#7879;u tr&igrave;nh. M&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; th&#432;&#7901;ng th&#7845;y l&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i cai thu&#7889;c d&#7915;ng vi&#7879;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng li&#7879;u ph&aacute;p thay th&#7871; qu&aacute; s&#7899;m v&agrave; sau &#273;&oacute; h&#7885; kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; ch&#7889;ng l&#7841;i c&#7843;m gi&aacute;c th&egrave;m thu&#7889;c&rdquo;.<br>
Ti&#7871;n s&#7929; McIntosh khuy&ecirc;n r&#7857;ng n&ecirc;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c li&#7879;u ph&aacute;p thay th&#7871; nicotine trong v&ograve;ng 2 &#273;&#7871;n 3 th&aacute;ng. V&agrave; sau khi d&#7915;ng li&#7879;u ph&aacute;p, b&#7841;n n&ecirc;n gi&#7919; v&agrave;i vi&ecirc;n k&#7865;o gum ho&#7863;c k&#7865;o ng&#7853;m trong t&uacute;i &#273;&#7875; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng khi b&#7841;n b&#7845;t ch&#7907;t th&egrave;m thu&#7889;c.</p>
<p><strong>Varenicline</strong><br>
L&agrave; lo&#7841;i thu&#7889;c cai thu&#7889;c l&aacute; m&#7899;i nh&#7845;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c FDA c&ocirc;ng nh&#7853;n, ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng d&#7921;a v&agrave;o vi&#7879;c ng&#259;n c&#7843;n vi&#7879;c c&#7843;m nh&#7853;n nicotine &#273;&#7871;n n&atilde;o. N&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&aacute;n v&#7899;i t&ecirc;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i Chantix t&#7841;i M&#7929; v&agrave; Champix &#7903; c&aacute;c n&#432;&#7899;c kh&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i. Chantix th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7881; &#273;&#7883;nh d&ugrave;ng trong 12 duy tr&igrave; trong 12 tu&#7847;n. Kho&#7843;ng 33% nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng Chantix &#273;&atilde; b&#7887; thu&#7889;c th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a class="dt-single-image" href="http://vapebienhoa.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Chantix.jpg" data-dt-img-description=""><img class=" wp-image-36089 aligncenter" src="http://vapebienhoa.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Chantix.jpg" alt="Chantix" width="600" height="364"></a>Thu&#7889;c cai thu&#7889;c l&aacute; Chantix</em></p>
<p>Chantix c&oacute; t&aacute;c d&#7909;ng l&agrave;m gi&#7843;m c&#7843;m gi&aacute;c th&egrave;m nicotine v&agrave; gi&uacute;p r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i b&#7887; thu&#7889;c l&aacute; th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng. Kh&ocirc;ng gi&#7889;ng nh&#432; Zyban, Chantix kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; d&ugrave;ng chung v&#7899;i c&aacute;c li&#7879;u ph&aacute;p thay th&#7871; nicotine (tr&#7915; khi c&oacute; ch&#7881; d&#7851;n c&#7911;a b&aacute;c s&#297;). Chantix &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&ecirc; duy&#7879;t n&#259;m 2006. C&aacute;c t&aacute;c d&#7909;ng ph&#7909; c&oacute; th&#7875; g&#7863;p khi d&ugrave;ng thu&#7889;c bao g&#7891;m bu&#7891;n n&ocirc;n, n&ocirc;n m&#7917;a, m&#417; b&#7845;t th&#432;&#7901;ng, t&aacute;o b&oacute;n v&agrave; &#273;&#7847;y h&#417;i. V&agrave;o n&#259;m 2009, FDA &#273;&atilde; y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u Chantix th&ecirc;m nh&#7919;ng c&#7843;nh b&aacute;o tr&ecirc;n h&#7897;p thu&#7889;c v&#7873; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7911;a th&#7847;n kinh nghi&ecirc;m tr&#7885;ng bao g&#7891;m tr&#7847;m c&#7843;m, &yacute; ngh&#297; mu&#7889;n t&#7921; s&aacute;t, h&agrave;nh vi t&#7921; s&aacute;t v&agrave; k&iacute;ch &#273;&#7897;ng. B&ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&oacute;, FDA cho r&#7857;ng nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng Chantix c&oacute; nguy c&#417; b&#7883; &#273;au tim v&agrave; &#273;&#7897;t qu&#7925; cao h&#417;n so v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&ocirc;ng d&ugrave;ng lo&#7841;i thu&#7889;c n&agrave;y. M&#7897;t s&#7889; t&aacute;c d&#7909;ng ph&#7909; nghi&ecirc;m tr&#7885;ng c&#7911;a thu&#7889;c c&oacute; th&#7875; li&ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n vi&#7879;c cai thu&#7889;c l&aacute;.</p>
<p><strong>L&#7901;i khuy&ecirc;n c&#7911;a chuy&ecirc;n gia:</strong></p>
<p>Gi&aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c Trung t&acirc;m Cai thu&#7889;c Leadership t&#7841;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;ai h&#7885;c California, San Francisco khuy&ecirc;n r&#7857;ng: <em>&ldquo;N&#7871;u b&#7841;n v&agrave; b&aacute;c s&#7929; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh th&#7917; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng Chantix, h&atilde;y ch&uacute; &yacute; &#273;&#7871;n t&acirc;m tr&#7841;ng c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh v&agrave; b&aacute;o cho b&aacute;c s&#7929; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c n&#7871;u th&#7845;y c&oacute; b&#7845;t c&#7913; thay &#273;&#7893;i b&#7845;t th&#432;&#7901;ng n&agrave;o. M&#7897;t s&#7889; t&aacute;c d&#7909;ng ph&#7909; &iacute;t nghi&ecirc;m tr&#7885;ng h&#417;n s&#7869; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n nh&#432; bu&#7891;n n&ocirc;n. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, c&aacute;c chi&#7879;u tr&#7913;ng s&#7869; gi&#7843;m d&#7847;n theo th&#7901;i gian&rdquo;.</em></p>
<p><strong>Zyban (Bupropion SR)</strong><br>
&#272;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p ph&eacute;p v&agrave;o n&#259;m 1997, c&#417; ch&#7871; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&#7911;a Zyban l&agrave; t&aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng h&oacute;a ch&#7845;t l&ecirc;n n&atilde;o &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;m b&#7899;t c&aacute;c tri&#7879;u ch&#7913;ng khi cai thu&#7889;c, v&agrave; gi&uacute;p cho ng&#432;&#7901;i nghi&#7879;n thu&#7889;c l&aacute; d&#7877; d&agrave;ng ch&#7889;ng l&#7841;i c&#7843;m gi&aacute;c th&egrave;m thu&#7889;c b&#7845;t ch&#7907;t. Thu&#7889;c th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c d&ugrave;ng 2 l&#7847;n m&#7897;t ng&agrave;y trong 12 tu&#7847;n. M&#7889;t s&#7889; ng&#432;&#7901;i c&#7847;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng Zyban trong th&#7901;i gian d&agrave;i h&#417;n. Kho&#7843;ng 24% ng&#432;&#7901;i nghi&#7879;n thu&#7889;c &#273;&atilde; b&#7887; thu&#7889;c th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng khi d&ugrave;ng Zyban.</p>
<p>Thu&#7889;c h&#7895; tr&#7907; cai thu&#7889;c l&aacute; Zyban</p>
<p>Zyban &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t c&oacute; hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i c&oacute; g&#7863;p ph&#7843;i tri&#7879;u ch&#7913;ng nghi&ecirc;m tr&#7885;ng khi cai thu&#7889;c. N&oacute; c&oacute; th&#7875; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ri&ecirc;ng bi&#7879;t ho&#7863;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p v&#7899;i c&aacute;c li&#7879;u ph&aacute;p thay th&#7871; nicotine kh&aacute;c nh&#432; mi&#7871;ng d&aacute;n ho&#7863;c k&#7865;o gum. FDA c&#361;ng y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u Zyban &#273;&#432;a c&#7843;nh b&aacute;o v&#7873; c&aacute;c t&aacute;c d&#7909;ng ph&#7909; nghi&ecirc;m tr&#7885;ng khi s&#7917; d&#7909;ng thu&#7889;c l&ecirc;n bao b&igrave; c&#7911;a thu&#7889;c, c&aacute;c t&aacute;c d&#7909;ng ph&#7909; n&agrave;y, c&#361;ng t&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; nh&#432; Chantix bao g&#7891;m tr&#7847;m c&#7843;m, &yacute; ngh&#297; mu&#7889;n t&#7921; s&aacute;t, h&agrave;nh vi t&#7921; s&aacute;t, k&iacute;ch &#273;&#7897;ng v&agrave; th&ugrave; &#273;&#7883;ch. M&#7897;t s&#7889; t&aacute;c d&#7909;ng ph&#7909; nghi&ecirc;m tr&#7885;ng c&#7911;a thu&#7889;c c&oacute; th&#7875; li&ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n vi&#7879;c cai thu&#7889;c l&aacute;. Thu&#7889;c n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng d&ugrave;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c cho nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i b&#7883; r&#7889;i lo&#7841;n co gi&#7853;t, &#259;n u&#7889;ng v&ocirc; &#273;&#7897;, bi&#7871;ng &#259;n hay nh&#7919;ng b&#7879;nh nh&acirc;n &#273;&#7897;t ng&#7897;t ng&#7915;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng r&#432;&#7907;u ho&#7863;c thu&#7889;c an th&#7847;n, ho&#7863;c nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;ang s&#7917; d&#7909;ng thu&#7889;c &#7913;c ch&#7871; monoamine oxit (MAO).</p>
<p>T&aacute;c d&#7909;ng ph&#7909; th&#432;&#7901;ng g&#7863;p nh&#7845;t l&agrave; kh&ocirc; mi&#7879;ng v&agrave; m&#7845;t ng&#7911;.</p>
<p>L&#7901;i khuy&ecirc;n c&#7911;a chuy&ecirc;n gia:</p>
<p><em>Thu&#7889;c Zyban n&ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u d&ugrave;ng 1 ho&#7863;c hai tu&#7847;n tr&#432;&#7899;c khi b&#7841;n cai thu&#7889;c &#273;&#7875; ch&#7871; ng&#7921; c&aacute;c tri&#7879;u ch&#7913;ng c&#7911;a vi&#7879;c cai thu&#7889;c. Gi&#7889;ng nh&#432; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i thu&#7889;c kh&aacute;c, Zyban n&ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng theo ch&#7881; &#273;&#7883;nh. H&atilde;y li&ecirc;n h&#7879; v&#7899;i c&#417; s&#7903; ch&#259;m s&oacute;c y t&#7871; ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c n&#7871;u b&#7841;n c&#7843;m th&#7845;y k&iacute;ch &#273;&#7897;ng, th&ugrave; &#273;&#7883;ch, t&acirc;m tr&#7841;ng ch&aacute;n n&#7843;n, c&aacute;c h&agrave;nh vi ho&#7863;c suy ngh&#297; mu&#7889;n t&#7921; t&#7917;, ho&#7863;c c&aacute;c thay &#273;&#7893;i kh&aacute;c trong suy ngh&#297; ho&#7863;c h&agrave;nh vi.</em></p>
<p><strong>T&#432; v&#7845;n v&agrave; h&#7895; tr&#7907;</strong><br>
Nh&oacute;m t&#432; v&#7845;n v&agrave; h&#7895; tr&#7907; &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7913;ng minh l&agrave; gi&uacute;p c&#7843;i thi&#7879;n th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng t&#7927; l&#7879; c&#7911;a m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i cai thu&#7889;c. C&oacute; nhi&#7873;u h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c t&#432; v&#7845;n kh&aacute;c nhau, l&#7901;i t&#432; v&#7845;n c&#7911;a b&aacute;c s&#7929; &#273;&#7871;n m&#7897;t ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh cai thu&#7889;c ch&iacute;nh th&#7913;c nh&#432; c&aacute;c ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c cung c&#7845;p b&#7903;i c&aacute;c trung t&acirc;m y t&#7871; v&agrave; t&#7893; ch&#7913;c y t&#7871; c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng. C&aacute;c d&#7883;ch v&#7909; h&#7895; tr&#7907; tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n d&#432;&#7899;i h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c cu&#7897;c g&#7885;i h&#7895; tr&#7907; (quitline) &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7913;ng minh l&agrave; r&#7845;t hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;. C&aacute;c d&#7883;ch v&#7909; t&#432; v&#7845;n th&#432;&#7901;ng bao g&#7891;m t&#432; v&#7845;n l&agrave;m th&#7871; n&agrave;o &#273;&#7875; nh&#7853;n ra h&uacute;t thu&#7889;c l&aacute;, c&aacute;c chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7875; ch&#7889;ng l&#7841;i c&#7843;m gi&aacute;c th&egrave;m thu&#7889;c, l&agrave;m sao &#273;&#7875; chu&#7849;n b&#7883; cho ng&agrave;y b&#7887; thu&#7889;c c&#7911;a b&#7841;n, c&aacute;c h&#7895; tr&#7907; trong su&#7889;t m&#7897;t th&aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n khi b&#7841;n b&#7887; thu&#7889;c v&agrave; nhi&#7873;u ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng tr&#7907; gi&uacute;p kh&aacute;c. D&#7883;ch v&#7909; t&#432; v&#7845;n c&oacute; th&#7875; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p v&#7899;i t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c cai thu&#7889;c kh&aacute;c.</p>
<p>T&#432; v&#7845;n v&agrave; h&#7895; tr&#7907; c&oacute; t&aacute;c d&#7909;ng v&ocirc; gi&aacute; v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i mu&#7889;n b&#7887; thu&#7889;c. S&#7903; th&iacute;ch c&aacute; nh&acirc;n l&agrave; ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute; quan tr&#7885;ng nh&#7845;t, do &#273;&oacute; h&atilde;y ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh m&agrave; b&#7841;n c&#7843;m th&#7845;y ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i m&igrave;nh. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n t&#7889;t trong m&ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng c&ocirc;ng ty c&ugrave;ng v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&aacute;c, h&atilde;y t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh cai thu&#7889;c c&oacute; li&ecirc;n h&#7879; v&#7899;i c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n t&#7921; cai thu&#7889;c m&#7897;t m&igrave;nh, h&atilde;y th&#7917; nh&#7919;ng nh&oacute;m h&#7895; tr&#7907; tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n v&agrave; Quitlines. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u b&#7857;ng vi&#7879;c truy c&#7853;p v&agrave;o Website c&#7911;a Vi&#7879;n Ung th&#432; qu&#7889;c gia v&#7873; cai thu&#7889;c ho&#7863;c C&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng Quitline B&#7855;c M&#7929;. B&#7841;n c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; g&#7885;i t&#7899;i &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&acirc;y quitline c&#7911;a nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c li&ecirc;n bang t&#7841;i 800- QUITNOW.</p>
<p>L&#7901;i khuy&ecirc;n c&#7911;a chuy&ecirc;n gia: <em>C&aacute;c nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u ch&#7881; ra r&#7857;ng b&#7841;n nh&#7853;n c&agrave;ng nhi&#7873;u s&#7921; h&#7895; tr&#7907; v&agrave; t&#432; v&#7845;n th&igrave; c&#417; h&#7897;i b&#7887; thu&#7889;c th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n c&agrave;ng cao.</em></p>
<p><strong>B&#7887; thu&#7889;c b&#7857;ng c&aacute;c bi&#7879;n ph&aacute;p cai thu&#7889;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p</strong><br>
Bi&#7879;n ph&aacute;p k&#7871;t h&#7907;p t&#7889;t nh&#7845;t ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; bi&#7879;n ph&aacute;p b&#7841;n th&#7845;y ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i b&#7843;n th&acirc;n m&igrave;nh. C&aacute;c chuy&ecirc;n gia cho r&#7857;ng ch&#7881; m&#7897;t s&#7889; h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n cai thu&#7889;c c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&uacute;p b&#7841;n v&agrave; b&aacute;c s&#7929; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n s&#7869; ch&#7885;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7919;ng chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; nh&#7845;t cho b&#7841;n.</p>
<p>N&#7871;u b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; th&#7917; v&agrave; th&#7845;t b&#7841;i khi c&#7889; g&#7855;ng cai thu&#7889;c b&#7857;ng m&#7897;t bi&#7879;n ph&aacute;p cai thu&#7889;c ri&ecirc;ng bi&#7879;t nh&#432; mi&#7871;ng d&aacute;n thay th&#7871; cho thu&#7889;c l&aacute;, th&igrave; s&#7869; t&#7889;t h&#417;n n&#7871;u b&#7841;n th&#7917; c&aacute;c ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p kh&aacute;c trong l&#7847;n cai thu&#7889;c ti&#7871;p theo.<br>
N&#7871;u nh&#7919;ng n&#7895; l&#7921;c cai thu&#7889;c tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&oacute; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n b&#7883; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c v&igrave; b&#7841;n c&#7843;m th&#7845;y qu&aacute; th&egrave;m thu&#7889;c, h&atilde;y n&oacute;i chuy&#7879;n v&#7899;i b&aacute;c s&#7929; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n v&#7873; vi&#7879;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c li&#7879;u ph&aacute;p cai thu&#7889;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p nh&#432; thu&#7889;c h&iacute;t thay th&#7871; thu&#7889;c l&aacute; v&agrave; c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i thu&#7889;c kh&aacute;c, bi&#7879;n ph&aacute;p n&agrave;y c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7871;n t&#7889;i thi&#7875;u c&#7843;m gi&aacute;c th&egrave;m thu&#7889;c.<br>
N&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng mu&#7889;n b&#7887; thu&#7889;c v&igrave; b&#7841;n lo l&#7855;ng v&#7873; vi&#7879;c t&#259;ng c&acirc;n, h&atilde;y n&oacute;i v&#7899;i b&aacute;c s&#7929; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n v&#7873; vi&#7879;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p &#273;i&#7873;u tr&#7883; &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;m thi&#7875;u vi&#7879;c t&#259;ng c&acirc;n nh&#7845;t, b&ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&oacute; h&atilde;y t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m l&#7901;i khuy&ecirc;n t&#7915; nh&#7919;ng nh&oacute;m h&#7895; tr&#7907;, nh&#7919;ng l&#7901;i khuy&ecirc;n n&agrave;y s&#7869; khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch b&#7841;n ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng h&#417;n.<br>
Cho d&ugrave; b&#7841;n l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n li&#7879;u ph&aacute;p &#273;i&#7873;u tr&#7883; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p n&agrave;o, h&atilde;y nh&#7899; r&#7857;ng b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u cai thu&#7889;c v&#7899;i m&#7897;t th&aacute;i &#273;&#7897; tinh th&#7847;n t&iacute;ch c&#7921;c. B&aacute;c s&#7929; y khoa, ti&#7871;n s&#7929; Bruce S.Rabin, Gi&aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c y khoa c&#7911;a Ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh s&#7889;ng kh&#7887;e thu&#7897;c &#272;&#7841;i h&#7885;c y khoa trung t&acirc;m Pittsburgh cho r&#7857;ng: &ldquo;L&#7841;c quan v&agrave; tin t&#432;&#7903;ng r&#7857;ng b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; s&#7913;c m&#7841;nh l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng&rdquo;.</p>
